{"article_id":"eM0bEAh6qgFUF50T","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump ' s quest","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to add a citizenship question to the 2020 census","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"ended Tuesday ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"with the administration caving on the plans ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"bowing to a Supreme Court ruling and an intractable time crunch .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"A Justice Department attorney , in an email","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that found its way onto Twitter ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"said","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"the department had finalized the questionnaire","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"and given the green light","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"to print it","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"without the citizenship question .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The decision is a symbolic blow to Mr. Trump ,","depth":3},{"id":13,"text":"who staked significant political capital on his ability","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"to get the question added","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"and who had said","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"it was \" ridiculous \" to conduct a census","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"without asking about citizenship .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"As late as Monday , the president told reporters","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"he was considering ordering an unprecedented delay of the 2020 count","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"to try to shoehorn the question into the form .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"But by Tuesday , the realities of the calendar and his administration ' s own legal positioning had set in .","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"\" We can confirm","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"that the decision has been made to print the 2020 Decennial Census questionnaire","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"without a citizenship question ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"and that the printer has been instructed to begin the printing process , \"","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"Kate Bailey , one of the Justice Department attorneys","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"involved in the case ,","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"said in the email","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"that found its way onto social media .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Adding the question was going to be a long shot","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"after the Supreme Court ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"led by Chief Justice John G. Roberts Jr. ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"erected a roadblock last week .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"The court ruled","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"while a citizenship question can be legal","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"- and indeed has been asked on the full census before -","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"the Trump administration cut too many corners","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"by adding it this time .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"The chief justice said","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"he doubted the explanations of Commerce Secretary Wilbur Ross for the need","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"to add the question .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"He called it \" contrived \"","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"and ordered a do-over .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"The only problem was that the administration told the court","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that it faced a June 30 deadline","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"- Sunday -","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"for finalizing the questionnaire","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and sending it to the printer .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Mr. Trump was faced with options","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"of either arguing","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"that the deadline wasn ' t real","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"or attempting to delay the census entirely ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"which would have invited a whole new round of legal battles .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Democrats ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"who accused Mr. Trump of trying to weaponize the census","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to suppress Hispanic and immigrant participation ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"cheered the president ' s failure .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"\" A citizenship question would have pushed us backward for nothing more than crass political calculations , \"","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"said Rep. Bill Pascrell Jr. , New Jersey Democrat .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"\" Today America won ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"and Donald Trump and his political minions lost . \"","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"The citizenship question had become a microcosm of the broader debate over Mr. Trump ' s approach to racial and immigration matters ,","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"and both sides turned up the rhetoric .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"\" Nobody can believe this ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"but they spend billions of dollars on the census ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"and you ' re not allowed to ask ? \"","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"an incredulous president told reporters Monday .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"He added :","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"\" There ' s a big difference , to me ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"between being a citizen of the United States and being an illegal . \"","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"Opposing Mr. Trump was the full array of liberal forces ,","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"including Democrat-led states , immigrant rights groups , civil rights organizations and progressive campaigns .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"\" The Trump administration ' s politically motivated efforts","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"to undermine the Constitution in this instance","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"were so reprehensible","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that even the conservative Supreme Court couldn ' t let them get away with it , \"","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"said Senate Minority Leader Charles E. Schumer , New York Democrat .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"The Trump administration seemed to have bungled the citizenship question effort from the start .","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"Mr. Ross said","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"he added it after a request from the Justice Department ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"which said","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"more specific citizenship data would help police voting rights laws .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"But evidence emerged","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"that Mr. Ross had been inclined to add the question before the Justice Department request","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"and had been in contact with Trump political allies","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"who had other reasons","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"for wanting the data .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Critics also said","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"the question ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"asked by this administration ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"would reduce the response rate .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Three district court judges ruled","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"that Mr. Ross ignored those findings","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"and cut too many other corners in his zeal","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"to get the question approved in time .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"The Supreme Court sped the case onto its docket","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"without waiting for circuit courts of appeals to rule .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"In a stunning decision last week , the severely divided court , in a 5-4 ruling , ordered Mr. Trump to take a do-over .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"But the ruling was handed down June 27 , three days before the deadline","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"for the census forms to go to print .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"Rep. Elijah E. Cummings , Maryland Democrat and chairman of the House Oversight and Reform Committee , said","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"the Supreme Court ' s decision was a victory ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"but he added","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"that he will continue an investigation","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"into why it was added in the first place .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"\" The attorney general and the secretary of commerce must now turn over all of the documents","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"our committee has subpoenaed on a bipartisan basis , \"","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Mr. Cummings said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":219,"left":127,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":121,"right":126,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":114,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":112,"right":113,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":111,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":111,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":116,"right":119,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":116,"left":115,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":8,"right":118,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":9,"right":117,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":12,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":122,"right":124,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":15,"right":123,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":138,"right":217,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":130,"right":137,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":21,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":18,"right":128,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":133,"right":136,"relation":"attribution"